
# Installation

The simplest way to install is via opam:

    opam init
    opam remote add xen-org git://github.com/xen-org/opam-repo-dev
    opam install squeezed

To build by hand first install dependencies:

    * OCaml
    * findlib
    * stdext
    * syslog
    * re
    * xcp
    * bisect_ppx

# Profiling for coverage

This code can be instrumented for code coverage. See
[COVERAGE.md](./COVERAGE.md) for details.

    make coverage
    make


